// F1.1: plan catalog for the per-USER `Subscription` model (buyers), which is
// a genuinely different product line from dealer plans above — a buyer's
// "ENTERPRISE" has no relationship to a dealer's "ENTERPRISE". Mirrors the
// values that were already being written as raw strings from
